::KitKat::

She looked at Destuctor and smiled. "I have faith in you. Don't let 
me down."  She turned and walked out of the lab.  She walked down the 
hall when she heard Drillbit's voice on her link.  "I'm heading to my 
quarters.  If you need to talk to me, I'll be there."

She finally reached the door to her room.  She walked in and sat down 
at her small desk.  She put her head down on the desk and sighed.  
She hoped against hope, that she was doing the right thing.  She 
sighed and lifted her head, looking at the bed, wondering is sleep 
was what she needed.  She shook head,"No, what I need is a small 
mmiracle from the matrix to pull this war off." She sighed and looked 
down. She was finally understanding just how lonely it was at the 
top.
